flowchart TD
    Start([Ticket Created]) --> ITSM[ITSM System]
    ITSM --> Webhook[Webhook Triggered]
    Webhook --> StoreWebhook[(Store Webhook Data<br/>PostgreSQL)]
    
    StoreWebhook --> TriggerPipeline[Trigger Pipeline]
    TriggerPipeline --> ExtractData[Extract Ticket Data<br/>- IP Address<br/>- Vendor Details<br/>- Location Name<br/>- Issue Type]
    
    ExtractData --> StoreTicket[(Store Ticket Details<br/>PostgreSQL)]
    StoreTicket --> DetermineSchedule{Issue Type?}
    
    DetermineSchedule -->|Link Down| Schedule1[Schedule: 2.5 min interval]
    DetermineSchedule -->|Link Degraded| Schedule2[Schedule: 5 min interval]
    
    Schedule1 --> LoopStart[Execution Loop<br/>4 iterations]
    Schedule2 --> LoopStart
    
    LoopStart --> LogExecution[(Log Execution Start<br/>PostgreSQL)]
    
    %% Parallel Data Collection
    LogExecution --> ParallelStart{Start Data Collection}
    
    ParallelStart --> APIFlow[API Data Collection]
    ParallelStart --> ManualTest[Manual Ping Tests]
    ParallelStart --> PlaywrightFlow[Playwright Screenshot]
    
    %% API Flow
    APIFlow --> FetchAPI[Fetch from API<br/>Based on Location]
    FetchAPI --> GetVendor[Get Vendor Name]
    GetVendor --> GetLinkID[Get Link ID]
    GetLinkID --> GetISPIP[Get ISP IP]
    GetISPIP --> FetchMetrics[Fetch Metrics using Timestamp<br/>- Jitter<br/>- Bandwidth<br/>- Packet Loss<br/>- Utilization]
    FetchMetrics --> APIComplete[API Data Collected]
    
    %% Manual Ping Test Flow
    ManualTest --> GetFirewallCreds[Get Firewall Credentials<br/>- Firewall IP<br/>- Username<br/>- Password]
    GetFirewallCreds --> EstablishConn[Establish Connection<br/>Netmiko/Paramiko]
    EstablishConn --> PingTest1[Test 1: Firewall → ISP<br/>Execute Ping Command]
    PingTest1 --> PingTest2[Test 2: ISP → Google DNS<br/>Execute Ping Command]
    PingTest2 --> CollectPingData[Collect Ping Results<br/>- Packet Loss<br/>- Jitter]
    CollectPingData --> ManualComplete[Manual Test Complete]
    
    %% Playwright Flow
    PlaywrightFlow --> LaunchBrowser[Launch Playwright Browser]
    LaunchBrowser --> LoginNMS[Login to Linkeye NMS]
    LoginNMS --> SearchVendor[Search by Vendor Name]
    SearchVendor --> CaptureScreenshot[Capture Screenshot<br/>- Utilization<br/>- Packet Loss<br/>- Jitter<br/>- Latency]
    CaptureScreenshot --> PlaywrightComplete[Screenshot Collected]
    
    %% Convergence Point
    APIComplete --> DataReady{All Data<br/>Collected?}
    ManualComplete --> DataReady
    PlaywrightComplete --> DataReady
    
    DataReady --> CorrelateData[Correlate Data Sources<br/>- API Metrics<br/>- Manual Ping Tests<br/>- NMS Screenshots]
    
    CorrelateData --> AnalyzeMetrics[Analyze Key Metrics<br/>Focus on:<br/>- Packet Loss<br/>- Jitter]
    
    AnalyzeMetrics --> ApplyThresholds[Apply Health Thresholds]
    
    ApplyThresholds --> HealthCheck{Link Status?}
    
    HealthCheck -->|Healthy| ResultHealthy[Result: Healthy]
    HealthCheck -->|Unhealthy| ResultUnhealthy[Result: Unhealthy]
    
    ResultHealthy --> StoreResult1[(Store Execution Result<br/>PostgreSQL)]
    ResultUnhealthy --> StoreResult2[(Store Execution Result<br/>PostgreSQL)]
    
    StoreResult1 --> LogAction1[(Log Actions Taken<br/>PostgreSQL)]
    StoreResult2 --> LogAction2[(Log Actions Taken<br/>PostgreSQL)]
    
    LogAction1 --> CheckIteration{Iteration Count?}
    LogAction2 --> CheckIteration
    
    CheckIteration -->|< 4 iterations| WaitInterval[Wait for Interval<br/>2.5 min or 5 min]
    WaitInterval --> LoopStart
    
    CheckIteration -->|4 iterations complete| FinalDecision{Final Status<br/>Analysis}
    
    FinalDecision -->|Consistently Healthy| CloseTicket[Close Ticket in ITSM]
    FinalDecision -->|Unhealthy Detected| RaiseTicket[Raise/Escalate Ticket]
    
    CloseTicket --> LogAck1[(Log Acknowledgement Time<br/>PostgreSQL)]
    RaiseTicket --> LogAck2[(Log Acknowledgement Time<br/>PostgreSQL)]
    
    LogAck1 --> End([Process Complete])
    LogAck2 --> End
    
    style Start fill:#90EE90
    style End fill:#FFB6C1
    style HealthCheck fill:#FFE4B5
    style FinalDecision fill:#FFE4B5
    style DetermineSchedule fill:#E6E6FA
    style DataReady fill:#E6E6FA
    style StoreWebhook fill:#87CEEB
    style StoreTicket fill:#87CEEB
    style LogExecution fill:#87CEEB
    style StoreResult1 fill:#87CEEB
    style StoreResult2 fill:#87CEEB
    style LogAction1 fill:#87CEEB
    style LogAction2 fill:#87CEEB
    style LogAck1 fill:#87CEEB
